<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="desire-n">desire <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'zaɪə(r)/    美 /dɪ'zaɪər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-urge">1.★ <strong>渴望；欲望(urge)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I am inspired by her courage and <strong>strong desire to</strong> succeed. 
她的勇气和对成功强烈的渴望激励着我。</p><footer>2012 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She had little <strong>desire for</strong> power.
她对权力没有什么欲望。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Confucius once said, “At seventy I can follow my heart’s desire.” 
孔子说过：“七十而从心所欲。”</p></div></div>